        <abstract>
            <p>He is going to S. America as captain of a ship. Offers to bring back fossils for CD and B. J. Sulivan.</p> 
<p>He is going to domesticate the Patagonian bird "something like a guinea fowl" in Sussex. He shot the only <hi rend="italic">Beagle</hi> specimen.</p> 
        </abstract>
